Given the JSON object:
[
  {"airline":"British Airways","price":200.0,"flight_number":"BA123"},
  {"airline":"Air France","price":180.0,"flight_number":"AF456"},
  {"airline":"EasyJet","price":150.0,"flight_number":"EJ789"}
]

{"airline":"EasyJet","price":150.0,"flight_number":"EJ789"}
Compute the total price for 2 passengers (price per ticket multiplied by 2). Output a JSON object with field total_price (number).
